dcterms:description: A dataset collected from observation sensors in the highway of Los Angeles County, using 207 sensors and 4 months of data dated from 1st Mar 2012 until 30th Jun 2012.
dcterms:title: METR-LA

dcterms:description: A dataset collected from Caltrans PeMS in Bay Area of California, containing 6 months of data from 325 sensors (nodes), which ranges from Jan 2017 to May 2017.
dcterms:title: PeMS-BAY
